<a itemprop="url" href="/tibetan-buddhism/glossary/s" title="Tibetan Buddhism glossary starting with s">(S)</a>

<a href="/definition/sumbharaja#tibetan-buddhism" title="Goto “Sumbharaja” definition">next»</a>]
